               <p>
            
               
                  <persName id="t16880831-12-defend76" type="defendantName">
                     Thomas 
                     Castle
                  <interp inst="t16880831-12-defend76" type="surname" value="Castle"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-defend76" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-defend76" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was Indicted for <rs id="t16880831-12-off59" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-off59" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-off59" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               picking the Pocket of 
                     <persName id="t16880831-12-victim77" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t16880831-12-viclabel60" type="occupation">Mrs.</rs>
                        <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880831-12-victim77 t16880831-12-viclabel60"></join> 
                        Peck
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-victim77" type="surname" value="Peck"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16880831-12-victim77" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880831-12-off59 t16880831-12-victim77"></join>
                     </persName>
                  
               
                  </rs>, wife of Mr. 
               <persName id="t16880831-12-person78">
                  Samuel 
                  Peck
               <interp inst="t16880831-12-person78" type="surname" value="Peck"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-person78" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-person78" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , on the <rs id="t16880831-12-cd61" type="crimeDate">22d. of August</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880831-12-off59 t16880831-12-cd61"></join>; as she was going along the Street in <placeName id="t16880831-12-crimeloc62">Cornhil</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t16880831-12-crimeloc62" type="placeName" value="Cornhil"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t16880831-12-crimeloc62" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880831-12-off59 t16880831-12-crimeloc62"></join>, he put his Hand in her Pocket and took away her Handkerchief, which the Prisoner could not much deny; and being known in Court to have been guilty of other Faults heretofore in the same manner, and pleading nothing effectual on his own behalf, he was found <rs id="t16880831-12-verdict63" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-verdict63" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880831-12-verdict63" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
